title: FEB 21 2022 - TRUDEAU TO SEEK EMERGENCY POWERS EXTENSION
description:
Far from declaring the crisis over, Trudeau doubles down on his quest to seek and extension on his  emergency powers, the woman trampled by Trudeau's forces during freedom protest is identified as an Indigenous elder, in his speech President Putin reveals that Russia will recognize breakaway republics in Donbass region and signed an order t deploy Russian military to the contested area, and lastly, a shooting at a Portland Antifa gathering has left 1 dead and 5 injured. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
